                     <interp inst="t18041024-50-person482" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            .) Is there a word of this true? - A. Not at all.</p>
               <p>The prisoner called one witness, who gave him a good character.</p>
               <p>GUILTY</p>
               <p>Of <rs id="t18041024-50-verdict259" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18041024-50-verdict259" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18041024-50-verdict259" type="verdictSubcategory" value="lesserOffence"></interp>
               stealing the goods, but not privately in the shop
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
